Class AttrManager

java.lang.Object
  temp.fibHeap.stixar.graph.attr.AttrManager

Direct Known Subclasses:

public class AttrManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements GraphAttrCollection

Implementation of graph attributes.

This class provides an implementation of the GraphAttrCollection interface. For details about managed and unmanaged attributes, please refer to the interface documentation.
